data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! This beautifully crafted residence offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and classic charm. Built in 2017, this home is designed to provide comfort and style for you and your family.
Key Features:

Interior Features:

Open-concept living spaces
Gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances
Spacious bedrooms with ample closet space
Master suite with a private bathroom
High ceilings and large windows for natural light

Exterior Features:

Well-maintained landscaping
Covered patio for outdoor entertaining
Two-car garage
Fenced backyard for privacy

Additional Amenities:

Energy-efficient design
Modern fixtures and finishes
Central heating and air conditioning
Easy access to the Creek Turnpike
Community: Broken Arrow school district
